{"tid":1364450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 元朗自治區對727發出不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-07-25T11:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:09:01.000Z","uid":255336,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e02fa18f67db0720ee969a528836008878ca2b3","tid":1364450,"uid":255336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"提晒水，大家識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】鄉議局主席劉業強表示，已責成元朗六鄉主席呼籲村民遊行當日不要外出。<br />\n<br />\n而早前要求警方不要發出不反對通知書的十八鄉主席程振明表示，遊行終點鄰近十八鄉，指遊行人士只要不超越鄉界，村民不會有行動。<br />\n<br />\n十八鄉主席程振明：「我們不會惹事，我們都不會怕事。你不挑釁我們，我們就不會理會你們，就算遊行自由發揮，我們都不會政治阻撓。」<br />\n<br />\n劉業強：「盡量勸喻村民遊行期間盡量不要外出，留在家中，以免與遊行人士有不必要的口角之爭。與此同時我們亦強烈呼籲，遊行人士要保持冷靜克制。」<br />\n<br />\n十八鄉主席︰遊行人士不越鄉界　村民不會有行動<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356729&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356729%26refer%3DShare&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6fQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=4b865aad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356729%26refer%3DShare&h=144bf187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356729&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"e425f88acedb27c64da4977d52ab07ce4fd6e98b","tid":1364450,"uid":255336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f74bec68c3094c5c66a14ef2c2ec0eaace0164d","tid":1364450,"uid":255336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgm